“We’ll be fine” she replies quickly, “Just keep ‘em back.”<br>
Kalasin takes Solari’s hand and swings it over her shoulder, helping the Queen to stand. She waits for the Queen to tell her what to do, unsure of how to handle a situation like this.<br>
